10 Apple's most important announcements at its iPhone 6s, iPad Pro event 
CIO: As expected, today's Apple event was chock-full of new products and interesting surprises. From brand new iPhones to a potentially game-changing Apple TV, there's no question that Apple is still operating at full throttle. Here is a rundown of Apple's most important announcements from the company's special event.
